\c 1
\s Kwaziso
\p
\v 1 Pauro, muapositori waJesu Kristu nokuda kwaMwari, kuvatsvene vari paEfeso, nokuna vakatendeka munaKristu Jesu:
\v 2 Nyasha kwamuri, norugare runobva kunaMwari Baba vedu naShe Jesu Kristu.
\s Mikomborero iri munaJesu Kristu, Musoro weKereke
\p
\v 3 Wakaropafadzwa Mwari naBaba vaShe wedu Jesu Kristu, wakatiropafadza nokuropafadza kose koMweya pazvinhu zvokudenga munaKristu,
\v 4 sezvaakatisarudza maari pasati pava nokuvambwa kwenyika, kuti tive vatsvene vasingasvoreki pamberi pake murudo;
\v 5 atitemera kare mukuitwa vanakomana naJesu Kristu kwaari, sezvaakafadzwa pakuda kwake,
\v 6 kuve kurumbidzwa kwenyasha dzake, madziri wakatiita kuti tigamuchirwe muMudikamwa;
\v 7 maari matine dzikunuro kubudikidza neropa rake, iko kukangamwirwa kokudarika, nokuda kwekuwanda kwenyasha dzake;
\v 8 madziri wakawanza kwatiri mukuchenjera kose noungwaru;
\v 9 atizivisa chakavanzika chokuda kwake, sekushuva kwake kwakanaka kwaakazvipira maari pachake;
\v 10 kuti pakuitika kokuzara kwenguva, avunganidze pamwe chete zvinhu zvose munaKristu zvose zviri kudenga, nezviri panyika maari.
\v 11 munaiye matakawanawo nhaka, yatakatemerwa kare nzviga zvaiye unoita zvinhu zvose nezano rokuda kwake;
\v 12 kuti tive verumbidzo yokubwinya kwake, isu takavimba kare kunaKristu;
\v 13 munaiye nemwiwo manzwa shoko rekubwinya reevhangeri yeruponeso rwenyu; munaiyewo matenda kwaari makasimbiswa noMweya Mutsvene wechivimbiso;
\v 14 uri rubatso rwenhaka yedu, \add kuratidza\add* rudzikunuro rwezvakawanikwa rwavanhu vaMwari chaivo, kurumbidzo yokurumbidzwa kwake.
\v 15 Saka nenivo, ndakati ndanzwa zvokutenda kwenyu munaShe Jesu, norudo kuvatsvene vose,
\v 16 handiregi kukuvongerai, ndichikutaurai paminyengetero yangu;
\v 17 kuti Mwari waShe wedu Jesu Kristu, Baba vokubwinya, akupei mweya wokuchenjera nokuzarurirwa paruzivo rwapamusoro pake;
\v 18 Muchivhenekerwa meso efungwa dzenyu kuti muzive kuti tariro yokudana kwake chii, nokuti fuma yokubwinya kwenhaka yake pavatsvene chii,
\v 19 nokti vukuru hwakapfuvurisa bwesimba rake kwatiri isu tinotenda chii, maererano nokubata kwesimba rake guru,
\v 20 raakashandisa munaKristu pakumumutsa kuvakafa, noku\add mu\add*garisa kuruoko rwake rworudyi  \add panzvimbo \add*dzokudenga.,
\v 21 kumusoro-soro kuutongi hwose noukuru, nesimba, novushe, nezita roga roga rinorebwa, pasati pari panyika ino chete, asi pane inozovuyavo;
\v 22 akaisa zvose pasi petsoka dzake, akamupa utungamiriri pamusoro pekereke iye, kuti ave musoro wazvose,
\v 23 ndiwo muviri wake, kuzara kwaiye unozadzisa zvose munavose.
